ğŸ”Œ 2. Wiring ESP32-CAM to FTDI Programmer
ESP32-CAM Pin	FTDI Programmer Pin
5V	5V
GND	GND
U0R (RX)	TX
U0T (TX)	RX
IO0	GND (only during programming)

ğŸ‘‰ Notes:

Connect IO0 â†’ GND when uploading code. Remove it after flashing.

ESP32-CAM can draw up to 300 mA â†’ make sure your FTDI can supply enough current.

