ğŸ› ï¸ 6. Troubleshooting (Root Guidance)
âš¡ Upload Issues

"Failed to connect" error â†’ check IO0 is grounded during upload, reset module once.

Wrong COM port â†’ check FTDI driver installed.

âš¡ Power Issues

ESP32-CAM keeps rebooting â†’ power supply too weak. Use separate 5V 1A supply if FTDI canâ€™t provide enough current.

âš¡ No Camera Found

Ensure correct board (AI Thinker ESP32-CAM).

Check #define CAMERA_MODEL_AI_THINKER is uncommented.

âš¡ Stream Laggy

Start with lower resolution (e.g., QVGA 320Ã—240).



ESP32 is not a high-speed camera board, so higher res (SVGA, XGA) reduces FPS.
